Kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse kw'ibyabaye mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abandura Coronavirus (COVID-19) urimo kwiyongera mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, ndetse n'Ubwongereza bwagaragaje ko mu gihe buri gihugu kiri mu bihe bitandukanye, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dushingiye ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bigomba kongera imyiteguro ku kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuziranenge.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari umuntu umwe w'indwara ya Hepatitis R, indwara itera indwara idasanzwe, y'inkomoko idasobanutse, yavuzwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Gukumira no Kurinda Indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye coronavirus ari ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, bugereranya coronavirus 2 y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibihamya ni uko 80% by'abarwaye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, bafite cyangwa badafite ibicurane, kandi abenshi muri abo barwayi barakira.
Mu barwayi 14 ku ijana ba COVID-19, uburwayi bwabo buteye imbere cyane bigatuma barwara cyane bigatuma baba bakeneye kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% barwaye cyane bigatuma baba bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi barekurwa bakajyanwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongereye muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza, tugereranya n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Nyuma yo gutera u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi yose muri iki gihe kirimo gukurikiza inzira y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi.
Mu nomero ya 5 ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri n'abandi batangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe mbere na mbere n'u Burayi, bishingiye ku mibare y'icyorezo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS).
Mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 ku bantu bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, aho ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ubu hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 39,768 banduye, kandi hapfuye abantu 1,727, muri bo 17,750 banduye, naho 1,441 bapfuye ni abo mu Butaliyani gusa.
Gufata umubare w'ibanze n'ibimenyetso by'ibanze by'umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) gitanga imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi yose, ituruka mu makuru y'ibiro by'ubutegetsi nk'inzego z'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima ku rwego rw'igihugu n'iz'akarere ndetse n'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima, buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yose yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi ndetse no mu Bwongereza, maze agereranywa n'ayavuye mu Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kugaragaza icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje, twabaze umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 uhereye ku ngengabihe isanzwe ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye mu bihugu byatangajwe ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imimerere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'i Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi igera kuri 14 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, ikurikirana neza iy'abanduye mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku Burayi bwose/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (inyandiko y'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'izamuka ry'umubare w'abanduye ryatangajwe n'Ubutaliyani, ariko ibihugu by'i Burayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye izamuka nk'iryo ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Igice cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Raporo igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutanga imibare y'abanduye, ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani, wari umaze ibyumweru bitatu cyangwa bike.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 igenda yiyongera cyane mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza.
Ibipimo byagaragaye mu cyorezo cya COVID-19 bigaragaza ko iki cyorezo kiri kwihuta mu bihugu byose.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bitandukanye biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, impinduka mu buryo bw'ubuzima rusange bw'igihugu n'imyumvire y'ibihugu bitandukanye ku bijyanye n'uburwayi, ndetse n'uburyo butandukanye bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu karere gakomeye k'u Butaliyani kazahajwe na COVID-19 batangaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru menshi avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi mu duce twazahajwe na COVID-19 byakoze uko bashoboye.
Amakuru ajyanye no kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi cyane ubu araboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku kigero cya 6% na 1% by'abarwayi (amakuru ntabwo agaragazwa).
Ariko kandi, zigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo zuzuze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi y'ibanze yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abamaze gupfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 201011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu bushobozi bwo gutanga ubutabazi bwitondewe n'ibitanda byo mu burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4.2 ku baturage 100,000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (ibibanza 12.5 by'ubutabazi n'ibitanda by'ubutabazi bw'urwego ruciriritse ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Ibimenyetso byerekana ko uburwayi bwo mu mutwe bufite aho buhuriye n'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe byatanzwe mu isesengura rishya ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 ku bagore batandatu ba ECDC, hagaragajwe ko mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Eurasia n'Ubwongereza, abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ibyago byo kurenza ubushobozi bwo gutanga ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bukabije &gt; 90%.
Kubera ko abenshi mu barwayi bagaragaye mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Burayi, mu karere k'ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bikorera abaturage bo mu karere runaka gusa, amakuru y'abanduye n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bigomba gutangwa ku izina ry'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ibarurishamibare cya 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu biriho, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku buzima rero, bigomba kwitwararika kugira ngo bitegure ibizamini bishya by'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage, bishobora kuba byatewe n'umuvuduko w'indwara, ndetse n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, nk'uko bimeze ku cyorezo cyibasiye ibice by'u Butaliyani.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu igenzura rishya ry'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwuzuye kandi bunonosoye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, aho guhinduka kuva ku gukumira ukagera ku kugabanya, mu gihe ukwiyongera k'umubare w'abanduye bishobora kutaha abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro igihe gihagije cyo kumenya, kwemera no gusubiza neza, niba bidakozwe hakiri kare.
Igeragezwa ryihuse ry'ibyago ryatumye hashyirwaho ingamba z'ubuzima rusange mu kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari umwanya muto cyane mu gihe ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu bikorwa by'ubuyobozi kugira ngo bigabanyirize ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Ibi biramutse bitabaye, uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima bw'ibihugu by'i Burayi, EU/Afurika y'Ubukungu bushobora guhura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kizazira indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) iterwa na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma abantu bahura n'amakuba.
Iyi virusi isa cyane n'indi ifite umwihariko wo kuba ifite ubwandu bw'indwara ya SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi barwara SARS mu 2003. SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu ducurama kandi igatera ibimenyetso bisa n'ibya SARS-CoV.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubukana buciriritse kurusha SARS, ariko yanduza cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, kandi abagabo barwaye cyane kurusha abagore.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo bigenda byiyongera kuri iki cyorezo, iyi nyandiko irashaka gutanga isesengura rihoraho kandi ryimbitse ku ngingo z'ubushakashatsi zigenda zihinduka vuba.
Tuzaganira ku bintu by'ibanze by'indwara, impamvu, indwara, gusuzuma, kuvura, kwitegura no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo ibibazo byinshi bikiri bitarashubijwe, twizeye ko iyi nyigo izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Umunsi mukuru wa Noheli yo mu mpeshyi ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye udasanzwe kandi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose, basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru no mu byumweru byakurikiye icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) mu 2003. Ni yo mpamvu yiswe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, izindi ndwara zifitanye isano zitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Icyorezo cyatangiye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yateje ubwandu bwa COVID-19 80000, abarwayi barenga 40,000 barekuwe mu bitaro, abarwayi barenga 3000 barapfuye.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryaburiye ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa rubanda wa mbere, kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, ubushakashatsi burenga 200 bwakozwe ku ndwara ya COVID-19, harimo kwiga virusi, ubwandu butera, gusuzuma no kuvura, kuva raporo ya mbere yatangazwa ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, igaragaza uko virusi yagiye itandukana n'abarwayi benshi.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusobanura neza iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu byiciro bishya by'amashami biri kuvugururwa mu buryo bwihuse.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS, indi ndwara iterwa na koronavirusi (CoV), ari yo MERS (indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati yaturutse mu 2012).
Tuzaganira kandi ku byo twize ku bijyanye no kwirinda no guhanura indwara, ndetse n'ibibazo dukeneye guhita dusubiza.
Ubusanzwe, virusi za CoV ni za virusi zitera indwara zitari ziteje akaga ku bantu, nyinshi muri zo zitera ibicurane by'ibicurane bigera kuri 15% by'ibicurane bya 4.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na koronavirusi zanduza abantu inshuro ebyiri, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye haduka icyorezo cya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, hanyuma zigera mu bindi bihugu byinshi ziteje akaga n'urupfu.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 ubu ni cyo cyorezo cya gatatu cya Coronavirus (CoV) mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1.1, umuganda w'abarwayi ba Hepatitis B bataramenyekana aho bakomoka, wabanje kubwirwa Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 uturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hasohotse urutonde rwa virusi ya corona (CoV).
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, impfu za mbere zaturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan zaratangajwe.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu buryo bwihuse mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, hatanzwe raporo y'ubwandu bw'abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima, byemeza ko ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu bushobora kubaho.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe nta modoka z'abantu bose zihageze.
