Imyaka: Imyaka ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi cyane mu kwemeza ko ushobora kurwara SARS na COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bafite imyaka 30-65, aho 47.7% by'abarwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
