Igitsina: Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore (0.31/100,000 na 0.27/100,000) nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Guhangayika no guhangayika: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane barushaho kurwara indwara z'umutima n'ibicurane bikomeye.
Impanuka z'umutima ni zo zikomeje kuba impamvu nyamukuru y'urupfu rw'abarwayi ba SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwinjiza mu bantu bafite indwara ya cholangioctues igira ACE2-positive, bigatuma ibwonko bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 butagira imikorere myiza.
Birakwiriye kandi ko tumenya ko imyaka n'uburwayi byombi bifitanye isano ikomeye, kandi ko bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bandi.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe byo mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi: Ibipimo bya poroteyine igira ibisubizo by'ubwoko bwa C (CRP) mu maraso bigaragaza uburemere bw'indwara cyangwa ibikomere by'ibisebe, kandi byatanzwe nk'ikimenyetso cy'uburwayi, gusubiza imiti no gukira vuba.
Ihuriro ry'ibipimo bya CRP n'uburemere bwa COVID-19 n'ubwiru na byo byaravuzwe.
Byongeye kandi, kongera lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu kwemeza ibisubizo.
Izi enzymes zigaragarira cyane mu bice bitandukanye by'umubiri, cyane cyane umutima n'umwijima, kandi zisohoka mu gihe cy'imikorere mibi.
