Muri rusange, RBD mu poroteyine S ya CoV ikorana n'indwara z'ibinure kandi iratoranywa mu gusubiza umubiri w'umuntu.
Muri SARS-CoV, RBD iri kuri amino acide 318 kugeza 510 ku gice cya S1 gifatanya na ACE2 y'umuntu ndetse n'indwara z'ibanze z'ubwandu bwa virusi.
RBD ya SARS-CoV ifite ubushobozi bwo kumenya ACE 2 receptor y'inyamaswa zitandukanye zirimo imbwa, imbeba, ingurube, imbeba n'imbwa, ibyo bikaba bituma virusi ishobora kwandura.
Mu by'ukuri, hari ibisigisigi 6 byonyine bya amino acide byabonetse mu buryo butandukanye n'ubw'ubundi bwa virusi y'umuntu na civet muri RBD, kandi 4 muri zo ziri mu murongo uhuza za récepteur kugira ngo zivugane na récepteur ACE2.
SARS-CoV mu nyamaswa ifite imiterere ya K479N na S487T mu RBD yayo, ishobora kongera ubushobozi bwo guhura kwa poroteyine nini n'indwara ya ACE2 mu bantu.
Ku bw'ibyo, gusimbuza izo amino acide zombi bishobora kuba ingenzi mu gutuma abantu barwara.
