Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryatangaje amabwiriza yihuse yo gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV), kandi ayo mabwiriza atanga uburambe bwacu n'inyandiko y'ibanze yo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Ariko icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni icyorezo gishya, ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite biragenda byiyongera bitewe n'ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu bikorwa. Ni yo mpamvu ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura zihora zigezweho.
Muri iyi nyandiko, twatanze igisubizo ku mabwiriza yacu kandi dutanga ibisobanuro bishya ku byerekeye "ibipimo by'ubwandu" n'"ibipimo by'ubwandu" nk'uko biteganywa n'amabwiriza ya nyuma yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Ivugururwa rya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Ubushinwa.
Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi iyi virusi yitwa indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero yitwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryashyizeho icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa virusi ya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryahise risohora amabwiriza kandi ashyirwa kuri interineti mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare ku ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Yateje impagarara kuva yashyizwe hanze.
Ariko kandi, zirikana ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, kandi ko ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bukomeza kwiyongera bitewe n'ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi, bityo ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura zigakomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yashyizweho na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abaturage y'Ubushinwa (ku ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020) yasohoye itangazo, ryasohotse mu bitabo birindwi, bimwe mu byo yasohotseho byahinduwe cyane.
Ubu, amabwiriza yacu yatanzwe na Zhou et al. batanze ibitekerezo byoroshye byo gutanga amanota bishingiye ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Umurimo wabo wongeyeho ibimenyetso bishya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi ni inyandiko y'ingenzi cyane ku cyorezo ku isi hose.
Turashyigikira umurimo wabo w'ingenzi kandi turabashimira.
