Umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga barwaye COVID-19 kandi ibipimo byabo byemezwa ko ari byiza, nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibiro bya leta.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarigeze kigenzura abaturage bacyo bagera kuri 3 ku ijana, kandi ibihugu byinshi byatanze amabwiriza y'agateganyo yo kudakora ibizamini ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje, urugero nka Italiya, U Buholandi, Esipanye n'Ubusuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwanditswe ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 batari barigeze bamenyekana, kandi ko ubwandu butanditswe ari bwo bwatumye haboneka 79% by'abanduye.
Isesengura ry'ibarurishamibare ryashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 30 Werurwe, ryatangaje ko umubare w'ubwandu mu Butaliyani urenze umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bugaragaza ko umubare w'ibanze w'ibisekuru (R0) bya COVID-19 ari 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, bwagaragaje ko bishoboka ko yazamukaho 5.7.
Abantu benshi barwaye COVID-19 bamaze gukira.
Mu bihugu bidafite ibimenyetso, igihe cyo guhangana n'indwara kugeza ku rupfu kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, aho ubusanzwe kiba iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 barapfuye bazize COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, guhera ku ya 5 Gashyantare, abagera kuri 80% by'abapfuye bari bafite imyaka 60 kuzamura, naho 75% bari barwaye indwara z'umutima n'ibyorezo bya diyabete. Umubare w'abapfuye ku buryo bwemewe n'amategeko kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange ni abapfuye basanze bafite COVID, nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibiro bya leta.
Umubare nyawo w'abapfuye bazize COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane kuko utabarirwa abantu bapfuye batakoze ibizamini - urugero nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi n'ibindi.
Ibipimo bimwe byo mu Butaliyani byagaragaje ko umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo urenze umubare w'abapfuye bose batangajwe n'ibiro by'ubutegetsi inshuro 4-5.
Abatanga amakuru ku kigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) bemeje ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] ari ugupfobya", amagambo yemejwe n'ibinyamakuru by'ibanze by'ibarura muri Amerika. Uko gupfobya akenshi biba mu gihe cy'icyorezo, urugero nk'icyorezo cya H1N1 mu 2009.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa bwagaragaye ku ya 1 Gashyantare mu gihugu cya Philippines, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya agaragazwa mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'u Bushinwa, abantu benshi bapfuye baranditswe muri Iran, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga mirongo ine byatangaje ko hapfuye abantu ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica.
Iyi mibare itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi igira ingaruka ku bipimo, ubuziranenge bw'ubuvuzi, amahitamo y'ubuvuzi, igihe kuva icyorezo cya mbere cyatangira, n'imiterere y'abaturage, nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange. Igaragaza umubare w'abapfa bagabanyijwemo n'umubare w'abanduye bagaragaye mu gihe runaka.
Dukurikije imibare ya Johns Hopkins University, igipimo cy'urupfu ku isi ni 6.0% (97,039/1617,204) ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Imibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'impfu yagabanutse iva kuri 17.3% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (ku bantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso nyuma ya 1 Gashyantare 2020).Ibindi ngamba harimo igipimo cy'impfu z'ibanze (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abamaze gusuzumwa bapfa bazize indwara, n'igipimo cy'impfu z'ubwandu (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye (bafite ibimenyetso n'abatarabifite) bapfuye bazize indwara.
Iyi mibare ntabwo yari ifite igihe kandi ikurikirana abaturage runaka kuva ku banduye kugeza ku barembye.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwagerageje kubara iyi mibare ku baturage runaka.
Ikigo cya Oxford University Centre for Evidence-based Medicine, giteganya ko umubare w'abandura muri iki cyorezo cyose uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibipimo biri hejuru y'urutonde birakurikiza ibisubizo by'ibizamini bya mbere bya COVID-19 mu Budage n'ibyigwa by'ibarurishamibare byerekana ingaruka z'ibizamini ku mibare ya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cyo kuruka no kurangiza ntabwo bizwi neza kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'ahantu.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Penn State, yavuze ko mu gihe nta buyobozi busanzwe buhari, ibyorezo byongera kwiyongera, hanyuma bigatangira kugabanuka iyo byamaze guhitana abantu.
Ariko biragoye cyane gukora ingero zifatika ubu ku gihe bizakorwa.
Zhong Nanshan, umujyanama wa leta y'Ubushinwa mu by'ubuvuzi, yavuze ko bishobora kurangira muri Kamena, mu gihe ibihugu byose byishyize hamwe bikakurikiza inama z'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ku bijyanye n'ingamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
"Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi bw'Ibihugu by'Ibirere n'Amahoro yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 ""ishobora gukomeza kwiyongera mu gihe cy'umwaka cyangwa ibiri""".
"Nk'uko byemejwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Imperial College, bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson, kwivuza no gufata izindi ngamba bizakenerwa ""kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rukoreshwa (hashobora kuba amezi 18 cyangwa arenga) """.
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yavuze ko "ntekereza ko bishoboka ko iyi koronavirusi" kuko imaze kwitegura kwanduzwa "itazongera gutakara burundu" kandi ko "ishobora guhinduka indwara y'igihe cyose, igashobora kugaruka buri mwaka".
Ibihe by'icyorezo bishobora kugaruka bitewe n'ubushobozi bw'abantu n'ubukana bw'ubwoko.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bitamenyekanye, kandi umuntu wanduye ashobora kuba nta bimenyetso agaragaza.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ubwoko bumwe ni ubushyuhe (88%) n'iseru ryumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara birimo umunaniro, guhumeka, guhumeka nabi, ububabare mu bice by'umubiri n'ingingo, kuribwa umutwe, kurwara imyanya y'umubiri, guhumeka, gukorora amaraso, kurwara impiswi cyangwa guhinduka ibara ry'uruhu. OMS ivuga ko umuntu umwe muri batandatu arwara indwara ikomeye kandi afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso by'indwara nk'ubuhumekero, ububabare mu gatuza cyangwa umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, kugira iseseme, no kugira ubururu mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa. Ubuvuzi bwihutirwa burasabwa niba ibi bimenyetso bihari. Gukomeza kw'uburwayi bishobora gutera indwara y'ibihaha ikomeye, ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero budafite ishingiro, indwara y'igifu, guhumeka nabi, no gupfa.
Abantu bamwe bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso, ariko bakagira ibizamini bigaragaza ko banduye virusi, bityo abashakashatsi bagatanga inama ko abantu bahuye cyane n'abantu banduye bagomba kugenzurwa no gukurikiranwa cyane kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Ubushinwa buvuga ko umubare w'abatarigaragaza ari muto cyane ku kigero cya 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo gusinzira (igihe hagati yo kwandura no gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso) ni umunsi umwe kugeza ku minsi 14, ariko muri rusange ni iminsi itanu. Urugero rw'ibihe bidashidikanywaho, imibare y'abantu barwaye COVID-19 batakaza impumuro bwa mbere ni 30% hanyuma ikagabanukaho 15%.
Hari ibindi bisobanuro by'uburyo iyi ndwara yandura bitaramenyekana.
Iyi ndwara y'igituntu y'ibinyigishi, bivugwa ko yandura cyane cyane mu gihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina ya bugufi, n'imyanda mito iterwa no gukorora, gukorora cyangwa kuvugana, mu gihe umuntu afitanye imishyikirano ya bugufi hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (metero 3 na metero 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukorora udategetse bishobora gutuma umunwa usohokera kure ya metero 4.5 (15 ft) kugeza kuri metero 8.2 (27 ft).
Hari abavuga ko virusi ishobora kwandura binyuze mu gusohora amazi make mu kirere, ashobora kubaho mu gihe umuntu avuga. Gusohora amazi mu gihe umuntu avuze, harimo no kuvuga, bishobora no guterwa n'umwuka nubwo virusi idashobora kwandura mu mwuka.
Amazi yo mu kanwa ashobora gutemba mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi, cyangwa se akagwa mu bihaha binyuze mu guhumeka.
Uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo kuvura, nko gutera amaraso mu bwonko no gukora CPR (cardiac resuscitation), bushobora gutuma umuntu ahumeka cyane, agahumeka cyane kandi bishobora gutuma agera mu mwuka.
Bishobora no gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku bintu byo ku mutwe, harimo n'uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso, izuru cyangwa akanwa.
Mu gihe hari impungenge ko ishobora gukwirakwira mu biremwa by'inyamaswa, iki kibazo cy'ubwandu bw'inyamaswa kivugwa ko ari gito.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanze ko virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 yandura mu kanwa. Iyi virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo ikwirakwira mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira no mu bihe bya nyuma by'indwara.
Abantu basuzumye bagasanga barwaye iyi ndwara mbere y'iminsi itatu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso, bigaragaza ko ubwandu bushobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'ingenzi bibaho.
Hari raporo nke z'abanduye batagaragaza ibimenyetso byemejwe na laboratwari, ariko ubwandu bw'indwara bwashyizwe ahagaragara n'ibihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gihe cy'iperereza rikurikirana.
