Udupfukamunwa dukoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwitarura abantu (cyangwa se byitwa kwitandukanya n'abandi) bikubiyemo ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu zigamije kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya abantu bahuye cyane.
Muri izo ngamba harimo gushyira abantu mu kato, gukumira ingendo no gufunga amashuri, aho bakorera, ibigo by'imikino, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibindi.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwitandukanya n'abandi mu kuguma mu rugo, mu ngendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, kwirinda guhura no kwihererana.
Ubu, leta nyinshi zirimo gushyiraho cyangwa zigatanga amabwiriza yo kwirinda mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
Umubare munini w'abantu bateranira hamwe, ugaragazwa n'ibigo bya leta n'imiryango y'ubuzima muri Amerika, wagabanyijwe byihuse kuva ku bantu 250 (niba nta COVID-19 y'akarere irimo) ukagera kuri 50, hanyuma ukagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza guteranira mu ruhame abantu babiri cyangwa barenga. Abakuze n'abafite indwara zirimo diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye kandi ziteza ibibazo byinshi. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza imvugo gutandukanya abantu n'ijambo gutandukanya abantu mu buryo bw'umubiri, kugira ngo bagaragaze ko intego ari ugugabanya ibyago byo guhuza umubiri, mu gihe bakomeza imishyikirano y'abantu hafi cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwirinda mu mibanire" byagize ingaruka ku bantu bagombye gushyikirana mu bwigunge busesuye aho kubatera inkunga yo gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo. Hari inzego zimwe na zimwe zatangaje amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina yo gukoresha muri iki cyorezo.
Muri ibyo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'abo ubana na bo gusa badafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Kwishyira ukwabo mu kato byasabwe ku bantu basanzwemo COVID-19 n'abakekwaho ubwandu.
Abashinzwe ubuzima batangaje amabwiriza arambuye ku byerekeye kwitarura abantu mu buryo bukwiriye. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose baba mu duce twanduye bakwirinda ubwabo.
Inama yo kwitarura abantu batandukanye yatangajwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragiranye isano n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19 n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere karimo ubwandu bukabije, basabwa kwihererana mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe baherukaga guhura n'umuntu.
Uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo ni ukugenzura, gukumira no kugabanya ubukana.
Ibi bikorwa bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye, ndetse no gutanga izindi ngamba zo kugenzura, gukwirakwiza no gukingira kugira ngo bahagarike ubwandu bukwirakwira mu baturage bose.
Iyo bidashobotse guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo, imbaraga zitangira kujya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: Ingamba zirafatwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka zacyo ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Uburyo bwo guhuza ibipimo by'ubuyobozi n'ubufasha mu kugabanya ubukana bushobora gukoreshwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira birasaba ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda icyorezo mu kugabanya umubare w'ibikomoka ku bimera ku kigero kiri munsi ya kimwe cya kabiri cy'abategetsi, ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura rigerageza kugabanya umubare munini w'ibikomoka ku bimera, bizwi nka "gukata umurongo w'ibikomoka ku bimera".
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kugira ibibazo mu nzego z'ubuzima kandi bigatanga igihe gihagije cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibipimo by'ubutabazi bidashingiye ku miti bishobora kugenzura iki cyorezo birimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'isuku y'intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwigunga, ingamba z'umuryango zigamije kwitandukanya n'umubiri, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro manini. Umuryango witabiriye ibikorwa byo gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibi bikorwa. Ibikorwa byinshi bigamije guhangana n'iki cyorezo byakozwe mu Bushinwa ubwo ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bwagendaga bwiyongera, nko gushyiraho ingendo mu mijyi yose no guhagarika ibikorwa bikomeye.
Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangiye kugenzura no gushyira mu kato abantu benshi ku mbuga nkoranyambaga no gutanga amabwiriza ku bimuka by'abantu banduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye, ikora siporo kandi igafatira ibihano bikomeye abatayikurikiza.
Taiwan yongereye ingano y'udupfukamunwa n'ibihano ku bicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi. Ingero z'Ubwongereza na Amerika zigaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya ariko kudasesa ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugihagarika (kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bakeneye ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko ikongera guhitana abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana, kandi inzego z'ubuzima zirasenyuka.
Ingamba z'ibikorwa zishobora gufatwa kandi zigomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ruhari), igihe ubwandu buza kwiyongera cyane mu gihe ingamba zizagabanuka.
Kuba nta ngamba z'igihe kirekire zashyizweho zo guhashya iki cyorezo, byateje ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wemewe gukoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19, ariko ibikorwa by'iterambere birakomeje, harimo no gupima imiti isanzwe.
Kunywa imiti igabanya ubushyuhe, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere, imiti ya ogisijeni, imiti y'umuyoboro wa intungamubiri n'imashini zifasha guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Gukoresha imiti ya Steroids bishobora gutuma ibisubizo birushaho kuba bibi.
Ingingo nyinshi zari zemejwe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwa virusi, zirimo gukorwaho iperereza kugira ngo zikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje kandi ko hari imiti gakondo n'imiti yo mu rugo ishobora kuvura ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
Kwita ku buzima no kubw'ibikenewe mu kwivuza no kwivuza COVID-19 byasobanuwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) nk'igisubizo cy'ibanze cy'icyorezo.
ECDC na OMS mu Burayi batangaje amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibindi bigo by'ubuzima by'ibanze yo guhindura ibikoresho ku rwego rw'ibanze, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa byo gupima COVID-19, gukuraho uburyo bwo guhitamo mu gihe gikwiriye, gushyira mu kato no kwihererana abantu banduye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi cyane cyane mu guhugura abakozi no kongera ibikoresho byo guhumeka n'ibitanda.
Hariho ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku cyatumye abanduye ba mbere (bitwa abarwayi ba zeru) batangira.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho kuba afite virusi nshya kandi idasanzwe ashobora kuba yarapfuye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abandura Zika muri Hubei wakomeje kwiyongera.
Abenshi muri abo barwayi bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, ryagurishaga n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi inyigo imwe yagaragaje ko virusi yavuye mu bwoko bw'inyamaswa muri izo, cyangwa se ko ishobora kuba yaraturutse ku nyamaswa. Icyorezo cy'ibicurane bitagira icyorezo cy'ibicurane cyakozwe ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, kivurwa na Dr. Zhang Jixian mu bitaro by'ibanze byo mu ntara ya Hubei, aho yamenyesheje ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cya Wuhan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, abaganga bo ku bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan babwiye bagenzi babo ko SARS ari virusi isa na coronavirus.
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bashyizwe ku rutonde rw'abapolisi bashinzwe gukwirakwiza ibihuha by'ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen ashinjwa ubugizi bwa nabi.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima y'umujyi wa Wuhan yaje gushyira ahagaragara itangazo ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha OMS.
Mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, abayobozi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan babwiwe ko hari abantu benshi barwaye ibicurane by'ibicurane. Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abarwaye wikubye kabiri mu minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze no mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, bitewe n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya wa China, kandi Wuhan ni ikigo cy'ibinyabiziga gikomeye n'ikigo cy'ubwikorezi bw'imihanda.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari abantu bashya bagera ku 140 buri munsi, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe i Shenzhen.
Nyuma, amakuru yemewe yerekanye ko abantu 6,174 batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarenze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani nk'igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abanduye barenga miliyoni 1.61 baratangajwe ku isi, abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abantu barenga 364,000 barakize.
Mu bihugu n'uturere 200 hirya no hino ku isi, hari nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cy'indwara muri Europe, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho igenzura ku mipaka.
Ibikorwa by'igihugu birimo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'igenzurwa ry'abantu bose (zwi ku izina rya Guma mu rugo, Guma mu rugo cyangwa Gufunga imiryango) n'ibihano byo gufunga imiryango. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu miliyoni 300 cyangwa abagera kuri 90% by'abatuye isi bari mu rugo. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, abagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1,3 bari mu kato mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo bwo gufungirwa mu rugo, biyongeraho miliyari 2.6 mu minsi ibiri yakurikiyeho, bangana na kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yabonetse kuva ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, kandi raporo idafite ibimenyetso byemeza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye yabaye ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr. Zhang Jixian yakurikiranye itsinda ry'abarwaye indwara y'ibihaha itaramenyekana ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, ibitaro bye byamenyesheje Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Isuzuma rya mbere ryagenewe ibipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryerekanye ko hari coronavirus nk'iyo SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
Umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) wabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
"Igihe ibi bimenyeshamakuru byatangwaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari baragabishijwe na polisi ko ""bakwirakwiza ibihuha"" by'icyorezo".
Komisiyo y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko nta bimenyetso bifatika byerekana ko abantu banduye.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukaze, bwaje kuvugwa na Xi Jinoing, umuyobozi w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, ko ari "intambara y'abantu" yo guhashya icyorezo.
Mu cyiswe "igikorwa cy'urugendo runini mu mateka y'abantu", gufunga kwatangajwe ku ya 23 Mutarama, guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan no hanze yawo, byongerewe ku mijyi 15 ya Herpe, bigira ingaruka ku baturage bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zirabujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya Muhire (Ubunani) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko hari kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byubatswe mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, ikindi bitaro, Ibitaro bya Leishenshan, byubatswe kugira ngo byite ku barwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bibanza 14 i Wuhan, nk'ikigo cy'inama n'ikibuga cy'imikino, ibi bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo guhangana n'ikwirakwira rya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera iminsi mikuru ya Noheli.
Kaminuza n'amashuri mu gihugu hose na byo byafunzwe.
Intara ya Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Imikorere ya kure yashyizweho mu bice byinshi by'u Bushinwa.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo zashyizweho mu gihugu no hanze ya Hobi.
Ibigo by'itumanaho rusange byarahindutse, kandi inzu ndangamurage z'ubushinwa zose zarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
"Gucunga urujya n'uruza rw'abantu mu baturage byarabujijwe mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byatekerejwe ko abaturage bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahura n'uburyo runaka bwo kuba hanze. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cyinjiriye mu cyiciro cy'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira virusi iturutse mu bindi bihugu".
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda y'iminsi 14 yo kwitarura abantu bose baturutse mu bindi bihugu binjiye muri uwo mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bw'ibanze bwagaragaje umuntu umwe gusa wanduye, mu minsi itanu yabanje, wari uturutse Istanbul yerekeza i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu mu gihugu ryahise rihagarikwa, kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Mu minsi imwe gusa y'igikorwa cyo guhagarika ingendo, ingendo zaragabanyijwe muri Hubei uretse muri Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri kuva ingendo zatangiye. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite visa cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizasubikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru arambuye y'igihe iryo tegeko rizarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa basabwa gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije inganda n'inganda gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku masosiyete. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo, utangira n'umwiherero w'iminota itatu ku rwego rw'igihugu saa kumi n'imwe za mu gitondo ku ya 4 Mata, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Shenzhen, nubwo leta nkuru yasabye imiryango gukurikiza interineti mu bikorwa byo kwitarura abantu kugira ngo birinde icyorezo cya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
