Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) kugira ngo bashyigikire ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'imiti, ndetse no kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo.
Ikigo cy'itangazamakuru Interaksyon cyatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko umudepite Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Singapore Red Cross yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni mu karere ka Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byihutirwa, u Burusiya bwohereje toni 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu karere ka Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko izatanga toni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Armenia yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo toni 10,000 z'imyenda, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, kandi Ubushinwa bwemeye gutanga amafaranga y'u Rwanda angana na miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika yo gufasha ibihugu byanduye.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho n'inzobere mu by'ubuvuzi kugira ngo bifashe u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'amasogisi miliyoni 6 n'udupfukamunwa 60,000 muri Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia kugira ngo bihabwe Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na za ventilate 5 muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje ko bitewe n'ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ibipimo byakozwe n'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yahagaritse ibikoresho 58,000 by'ubushakashatsi bwa Coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa kubera ko bifite 30% by'ubwiru gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwisubije 600,000 by'udupfukamunwa tw'ubushakashatsi twakozwe n'Ubushinwa.
U Bubiligi bwamaze gukusanya udupfukamunwa 100,000 tw'ikoranabuhanga, twitwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha bw'ibihe bidasanzwe ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rishimye cyane imbaraga z'abategetsi b'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryagaragaje itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS mu 2002-2004 aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye batabasha guhashya no gukumira iki kibazo, n'ikibazo cy'ubu aho leta nkuru  yatanze amabwiriza yo kugenzura kugira ngo birinde urujijo mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bukuru cyo gushyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS, Gauden Galea, yavuze ko nubwo "ntago ari inama yatanzwe na OMS", ariko ko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo kwiyemeza guhashya icyorezo aho cyiganje cyane, kandi ko icyorezo kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ubwandu bw'abantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'ibyago mu bindi bihugu, umuyobozi wa OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cy'indwara y'uburwayi ku isi kuva icyorezo cya mbere cy'indwara y'uburwayi cyatangira mu 2009.
Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, yavuze ko PHEIC iterwa n'ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abiciriritse, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
"Mu gusubiza ku itegeko ribuza ingendo, Tedros yemeje ko ""nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi bidafite akamaro"" kandi ko ""WHO idatanga inama yo guhagarika ubucuruzi n'ingendo""".
"Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira uburyo bwo kwitegura mu buryo bw'ibanze mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ibihe bidasanzwe, mu gufasha ibihugu bidafite uburyo bwo gushaka abantu banduye virusi, nubwo byazamutse""".
"Tedros yakomeje avuga ko ""ibihugu byose, hamwe n'umuntu umwe ufite intege nke, bingana n'abandi bose"" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga ""gushora imari uyu munsi, cyangwa se ugatakaza byinshi nyuma"." Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku ya 11 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryise icyorezo COVID-19".
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yemeje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, António Guterres, yemeye guha ububasha umuryango wose wa Loni mu guhangana.
"Itsinda ry'ubuyobozi bw'ibiza rya ONU ryarashinzwe, bituma habaho guhuza ibisubizo bya ONU byose, aho OMS izabafasha kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gutanga ubumenyi bwabo mu gushyigikira ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abantu ku iterambere ry'icyorezo""".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rya WHO ryahuje ingendo n'u Bushinwa ryashyizweho kugira ngo rihe inzobere mpuzamahanga na WHO amakuru y'imiterere y'iki cyorezo mu Bushinwa, kugira ngo bifashe mu gucunga indwara mu karere no gusuzuma kugerwaho n'icyorezo no kubasha kucyandura, hashyirwaho amahugurwa n'inama n'ibigo by'ibanze ku rwego rw'igihugu, kandi hakorwa ingendo z'ubushakashatsi kugira ngo bamenye imbaraga z'ibikorwa byo guhangana ku rwego rw'intara n'akarere, harimo n'ibyaro n'imidugudu. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko isi yose ikwiye gufata ingamba zikomeye zo kwitegura icyorezo cya Coronavirus, ivuga ko mu gihe iki cyorezo kigiye kwiyongera mu bihugu byose, abantu bose bagomba kwitegura.
