Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko habayeho icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS ifite impungenge zikomeye kubera igipimo cy'ibyago byo gukwirakwira no gukomera, ndetse n'ibyago byo kutagira icyo ikora.OMS yanenzwe cyane kubera ko nta buryo buhagije bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo, harimo gutangaza mu buryo bukomeye ibyago by'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu byorezo.
Ibisubizo byakubiyemo icyifuzo cya Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, cyo gusaba ko yegura, cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu zigera kuri mirongo zashyize imbaraga ku kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa muntu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Abahanga bavuga ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gutabara ubuzima kandi ko leta ari yo igomba kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura ibikoresho cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba gufatwa nk'impamvu yo kwamagana itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, harimo abafite ubumuga, abari mu moko mato mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abantu bavuye mu byabo ku mipaka, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bihe bidasanzwe, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda y'abantu badafite ibyangombwa bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Umuryango mpuzamahanga urimo gusuzuma ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage z'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishyirahamwe ry'Ubukungu n'Ubutwererane n'Iterambere ryatangije uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru agezweho kandi yimbitse ku bisubizo by'ingamba mu bihugu byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Mu rwego rwo gukomeza gahunda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi, mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibihe by'impunzi no kugabanya ingendo, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga, hamwe na gahunda z'igihugu z'ikurikirana politiki, bigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no koroshya ibisubizo by'isi byose byuzuye ibibazo bya coronavirus.
