Ubutegetsi bwa Amerika buyobowe na Donald Trump bwise coronavirus "Virus y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan", buvuga ko "gufunga u Bushinwa virusi ubu yarahindutse icyorezo ku isi" byamaganwe nk'ivangura rishingiye ku moko kandi "byerekana ko ubutegetsi bwe bwananiwe guhangana n'iki cyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyabonye ibimenyetso bya leta ya Amerika byerekana ko hari amayeri y'itumanaho akomoka mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, aho bavuga ko "byose byerekeye Ubushinwa".
Ibi kandi byerekana ko tugomba kugerageza no gutanga ubutumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'ibiterane by'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo.Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byemeje ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu birimo virusi ari kimwe mu bituma ubukangurambaga bukomeza ku isi hose.
