Byatumye kandi ku isi hose habaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kuko OMS yaburiye ko bishobora guteza akaga ku bakozi b'ubuzima.
Muri Australia, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bacuruzi basanzwe yo kugurisha ibicuruzwa by'igihugu mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye habaho ibura ry'amata, amata y'impinja ku masoko y'ubucuruzi, ndetse amaherezo leta ya Australia irabyanga. Nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyari gikomeye mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, kandi hakomeje kubaho kwiyongera kw'ibyifuzo by'ibiribwa, utwo turere twombi twaravanweho ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba z'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi bw'ibikomoka ku binyabutabire n'ibikomoka ku binyabutabire zageze ku ntego, zirinze ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa byera byitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
U Butaliyani bw'Amajyaruguru, umusaruro w'ubuhinzi w'ingenzi ntiwagabanutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera, nk'uko byemezwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Ibicuruzwa by'ibiribwa byarabuze mu gihe gito ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa batanze inyama z'ingurube z'ibitunguru kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya.
Amategeko nk'aya aboneka mu Butaliyani asaba abakora ibiribwa kubitegurira ibyo bihe by'impanuka.
