Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara y'ubuhumekero y'ubwoko bushya ya 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi itera SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura ko virusi ihari n'ubundi bwo gutahura ko hari imyanya ndangagitsina ikorwa mu guhangana n'ubwandu.
Kuba virusi yari mu cyitegererezo byemejwe na RT-PCR (Reaction de la chaîne polymère de transcription perturbée) igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kizamini ni cyihariye kandi kigamije gutahura gusa RNA ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu cyangwa ubwandu bushya.
Igishushanyo cy'umubiri (serology) gishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no gusuzuma abaturage.
Ibizamini bya Antibody bigaragaza umubare w'abantu barwaye iyi ndwara, harimo abataragaragaza ibimenyetso n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ibipimo by'ubukana bw'indwara n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bishobora kumenyekana neza binyuze mu gupima ibipimo.
Kubera ko ibizamini byari bike muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku kigero cya virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi habayeho itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibipimo byakozwe mu gihugu cyose.
Ibi kandi bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa mu barwayi bavugwa, bikaba bishoboka ko mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe byarenze ibipimo.
Hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rya Real-Time Transmission of Transmission of Transmission (rRT-PCR) polymerase chain reaction, ibizamini bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byavanywe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo by'amahembe, ibipimo by'amahembe cyangwa ibipimo by'ibice by'ubuhumekero.
Ibisubizo muri rusange bishobora kuboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi ibiri.
Ibizamini bya RT-PCR bikorwa hamwe n'imyanya y'ubuhumekero ni byo byiringirwa mu byumweru bya mbere by'indwara.
Nyuma, virusi ishobora gusubira mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu gihe ikomeza kugera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibikoresho by'isubiramo bishobora gutorwa mu mwuka mu buryo bwimbitse, hakoreshejwe udupira tw'amaboko cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukoropa (amasazi).
Imwe mu ngero za mbere za PCR yatangijwe i Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020, ikoresha uburyo bwa Real-Time Transmission-Related Polymerase Chain Reaction (rRT-PCR), kandi yashyizeho base ya 250,000 yo gukwirakwiza na OMS.
