Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kubera COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kubera COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gushyira mu bikorwa amabwiriza y'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Igenzura ry'ibyago mu kazi rishingiye ku kazi n'aho ukorera, rishingiye ku gusuzuma ibyago bituruka ku mwuka, uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye ushobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi k'ibyago bike gafite imikoranire micye n'abaturage n'abandi bakozi, hagirwa inama yo gukoresha ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, guhumeka nabi no gukomeza isuku no kwanduza indwara mu kazi.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura mu buryo bworoheje, harimo abakenera guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera abantu batazi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo birimo abakozi bafatanya n'abaturage muri rusange, nk'abanyeshuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo hari abaturage benshi, n'ahandi hantu ho gucuruza hakorerwa ibintu by'agaciro.
Kugabanya ibyago by'iki cyorezo byiyongera ku ngamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo guhumeka neza ukoresheje imashini z'ubwiherero zikora neza, indorerwamo z'ibikoma no kwambara ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu ashobora guhura na byo mu gihe afashwe na COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu buvuzi n'abashinzwe imirambo bazi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 ko bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, iyo abakozi bakora imikorere yo gukora urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima cyangwa gukusanya cyangwa gutunganya ibipimo by'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Gucunga ibyago by'abo bakozi birimo gucunga ibyuma by'ubwubatsi, nk'icyumba cy'umwuka gifite umuvuduko utaboneye hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaba ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ingaruka zishobora guterwa n'ibyo.
Urutonde rw'ubucuruzi rushobora guhinduka haba mu bijyanye n'ibyo ibicuruzwa bisabwa n'uburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (urugero, kugura ibicuruzwa mu masaha y'ikirenga cyangwa binyuze mu gutwara abantu cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara abantu).
Amaherezo, ingendo z'ibicuruzwa ziturutse mu turere tuzwiho kuba twatewe na Covid-19 zarahagaritswe. Imigambi y'ibisubizo n'imyitwarire ishobora gukoreshwa mu gutanga amabwiriza y'ibikorwa by'ubutabazi.
Gahunda yo guhangana n'ibipimo by'ibyago bijyanye n'akazi n'inshingano zitandukanye, harimo isoko y'ibyago, ibyago bituruka ku mazu n'imiryango, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye, nk'imyaka cyangwa ubuzima bubi.
Banasobanuye uburyo bwo gucunga bukenewe mu guhangana n'ibyo byago no gutegura uko ibintu byagenda mu gihe habayeho icyorezo.
Kwitegura no guhangana n'icyorezo bishobora kuba ibya komisiyo y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo harimo kugabanya ibyifuzo by'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara, kubungabunga ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo mu ikoranabuhanga ryabo.
Ibibazo by'indwara mu baturage byatewe n'ubucuruzi mu duce twazahajwe n'iyo ndwara.
Gucunga ibiza ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu buzima n'umutekano mu kazi mu gucunga neza ibyago by'itsinda.
Mu gihe ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga, bukurikiraho ni ubuyobozi n'ibikoresho bya nyuma byo kwirinda.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubwubatsi burimo guhagarika abakozi mu kaga gakomeye gaherekejwe n'akazi, ntibufite aho buhuriye n'imyitwarire y'abakozi kandi bushobora kuba umuti mwiza cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ubuyobozi ni ihinduka ry'amahame cyangwa imikorere y'akazi, bisaba ko habaho igikorwa cy'umukozi, umukozi cyangwa umukoresha.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora cyane kurusha ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda bimwe mu bibazo.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku byago bigera ku bakozi, abakozi bafite ibikoresho bikwiye (urugero: ibikoresho byo guhumeka), bambaye neza kandi neza, basuzumwa buri gihe, bakitabwaho kandi bagasimbuzwa igihe bibaye ngombwa, kandi bakurwaho neza, bakanahumurwa, bakabikwa cyangwa bagatabwa kugira ngo birinde kwanduzanya.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano (OSHA), akazi k'ibyago bike gafite imikoranire mike n'abaturage n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura zasabwe ku kazi zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi no gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, guhumeka nabi harimo no gukorora no kwitsamura, gutanga udupira n'udupfunyika, gutegura telefoni cyangwa guhindura indimu niba ari ngombwa, kudashishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi no gukomeza isuku no kwanduza indwara zisanzwe z'aho bakorera.
Kumenya abantu bashobora kwandura no kubatandukanya n'abandi ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gisaba ko abakozi bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bafite umuriro mwinshi, umuriro mwinshi n'ibindi bimenyetso by'uburwayi mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 nta muti wo kugabanya umuriro cyangwa undi muti uhindura ibimenyetso, kandi amategeko yo kureka akazi kubera uburwayi ashobora gukurwaho, yemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita kuri umwe mu bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi abakozi bagomba kumenya ayo mategeko.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, akazi k'ibyago byo kwandura gisanzwe gakubiyemo abakenera guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegera cyane abantu bataramenyekana cyangwa bakekwaho kurwara COVID-19 ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje kuba mu baturage bakikije ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi, cyangwa bitewe n'uko uwo muntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Ibi bikubiyemo abakozi bafatanya n'abaturage muri rusange, nk'abo mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo, umubare munini w'abaturage, n'ibipimo by'ubucuruzi biri hejuru. Ubuyobozi bw'ubwubatsi kuri iri tsinda n'itsinda ry'ibyago birimo gushyiraho umwuka mwiza, kongera umuvuduko w'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi nk'ibikoresho byo guhuma, ibifunga amaso no gushyiraho ibifunga imodoka ku bakiriya, gushyiraho amabwiriza mashya ku bakozi, gushyiraho amabwiriza mashya ku bakozi, kurinda abakozi cyangwa abakozi COVID-19, hamwe no kwigisha abakozi kwirinda indwara, hamwe no gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Abakozi bari mu itsinda ry'ibyago ntibakenera gukoresha ibyuma byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, kugenzura neza kugira ngo abakozi n'abandi bagenzi birinde, harimo gutandukanya umuntu urwaye n'abandi mu ntera ya metero 6, guha umukozi w'ubutabazi umurwayi no kumuha agapfukamunwa, cyangwa gusaba umurwayi gufunga umunwa n'amazuru igihe akoroye cyangwa ahekenya.
Abagenzi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dushobora kujugunywa nyuma yo gukoreshwa mu gihe bita ku bagenzi barwaye cyangwa bafite ibiyobyabwenge ku mubiri, kandi bashobora kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'inyongera mu gihe bagwaye umuriro, ikimwaro kidashira cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Ibikoresho byo munsi y'amaboko n'ibindi bintu bikwiye kujugunywa bigomba kujugunywa mu gikapu cya biofuel, kandi imbaho z'ibinyabutabire zigomba gusukurwa no guhumanywa. Ku ngendo z'ubucuruzi, harimo ubwato bw'ingenzi n'ubundi butwara abagenzi, kugenzura impanuka birimo gutinda urugendo igihe urwaye, kwigunga no kubwira ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu ndege byihuse niba hari umuntu ufite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso igihe ari mu ndege.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, ubugenzuzi bw'ubuvuzi bugomba kubera mu byumba by'abantu badafite aho bahurira n'abandi. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC irasaba ko hafungwa by'agateganyo kugira ngo hasuzumwe cyangwa hakurweho imiti yica udukoko iyo umuntu yanduye ari mu nyubako z'ishuri, hatitawe ku cyorezo cy'ubwandu mu baturage.
Iyo hari abantu bake cyane mu baturage, ingamba zo kwitarura abandi zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, nko kureka kujya mu kibuga, inama n'andi materaniro manini, urugero nk'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa amasomo ya orchestre, cyangwa kurya muri cafeteria, kongera intera hagati y'ameza, kuzana no kwirukana abashyitsi, kugabanya umubare w'abashyitsi batagikenewe, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho kwivuza ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'ibicurane.
Iyo hari uburyo bwinshi bwo gutwara abantu mu baturage baho, usibye ingamba zo guhangana n'imibereho, imyitozo y'amashuri yagutse ishobora gusuzumwa. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bya buri munsi, ubuzima bufatwa nk'ubw'ibyago bicye na CDC.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'abantu bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 barasabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bukwiye.
Iyo umuntu atandukanye n'abandi mu gihe cy'akababaro, umukozi agomba gusukura no kuvura udukingirizo n'udupfunyika mbere yo kudukoresha, akoresheje indimu cyangwa isuku, kandi akurikiza amabwiriza yo kubika no kujugunya ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byakoreshejwe, hamwe no kubika no guhanagura imyenda.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abashinzwe imirambo bamwe mu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Imirimo y'ibyago byinshi ikubiyemo gutanga serivisi z'ubuzima, gutanga ubufasha mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi no gutwara abaganga, abazwiho kuba barwaye COVID-19.
Ibi byabaye ibyago bikomeye cyane niba abakozi bakora inzira yo guhumeka cyangwa gukusanya cyangwa gufata ibipimo ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Uburyo bwo gutandukanya ibintu bikomeye cyangwa by'imyanda mu mwuka, harimo guterwa, uburyo bwo gukorora, kureba ibihaha, uburyo bwo gusuzuma amenyo cyangwa gutoragura ibipimo by'ibihaha.
Imirimo yo mu marimbi ifite ibyago byinshi, harimo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imirambo y'abantu bazi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 igihe bapfaga. Ibi byose biteza ibyago byinshi niba babikesha ubuhanga. Ibirimo gukorwa by'ubwubatsi byiyongereye kuri ibi byiciro by'ibyago birimo nk'icyumba cyo kwihereramo abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, harimo n'igihe hashyizweho uburyo bwo gukora ibikoresho birimo ibintu by'imyanda bishobora guturika.
Ihingwa ry'umwuka rifite imbaraga nyinshi rishobora kuba rikwiriye mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bimwe na bimwe no mu matongo.
Ibizamini bigomba kugenzurwa mbere y'uko bifatwa kubera umutekano muke w'icyiciro cya 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryasabye ko abarwayi binjira mu gihugu batandukanywa mu byumba bitandukanye byo gutegereza bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Byongeye kandi, ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri (PPE) OSHA itera inkunga gukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka ku bantu bakorera ku ntera ya metero 6 z'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho SARS-CoV-2 n'abandi bose bakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero twemewe na NIOSH twitwa N95 cyangwa se Better, dukoreshwa mu buryo bw'uburyo butandukanye bw'ubuvuzi bw'ubuhumekero bufite ibisobanuro byimbitse, burimo gupimwa, gutozwa no kubagwa.
Ubundi buryo bwo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi bugatuma abakozi barushaho kugira ubuzima bwiza. OMS ntiyifuza ko abantu bambara imyenda y'imbere, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yanduza mu myanya y'ubuhumekero aho kwanduzwa n'amazi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko udupfukamunwa two mu maso two kwa muganga dukoreshwa n'abakozi bareba aho binjira gusa.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, abitaho cyangwa batwara abarwayi ba COVID-19 badafite uburyo bwo gutunganya ibintu bikomeye cyangwa by'amazi mu byuka, OMS irasaba ko bakoresha udupfukamunwa, udupfukamunwa tw'amaso cyangwa udupfukamunwa, amakanzu n'amaboko.
Uburyo bwo kuvugurura ibintu bikomeye cyangwa by'amazi mu byuka ni bwo bwakoreshejwe, ibipfukamunwa bya muganga byafashwe n'ibipfukamunwa bya N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho bya PPE ku isi yose bidahagije, OMS irasaba kugabanya ibisabwa mu bijyanye na PPE hifashishijwe telemedicine, ibikoresho by'umubiri nk'idirishya ry'amaso, kwemerera gusa abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi kwinjira mu cyumba kirimo abarwayi ba COVID-19, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho bya PPE bikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukomeza gukoresha ibikoresho bimwe by'ubuhumekero bitagomba gutwara igihe bita ku barwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza umurongo w'itangwa rya PPE no gushishikariza gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso.
