ACE2 ni imwe muri za enzymes ziba ku mibiri y'ibihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu nda.
ACE2 ikumira ibikorwa bya ACE (Autotropin-binding enzyme) bifitanye isano no kugabanya ingano ya ACE-II no kongera Ang ((1-7)), bigatuma iba umuti ugamije kuvura indwara y'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'aho yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za virusi runaka.
Abantu bafite ubwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo, akenshi bita hACE2.
Enzyme ikuraho ingufu 2 ni uruziga rufite ibyuma, ruri ku mbuga z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'imbere n'iz'inyuma.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 itwara igice cya N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na acid transporter domain mu buryo bwa C-terminal collagen.
ACE2 ni inzira ya mbere yo gutangiza poroteyine, aho poroteyine igira uruhare rwihariye ku mibiri y'ibihaha n'indi mibiri.
Uru rugingo rw'inyongera rwa ACE2 rwatandukanyijwe n'uru rugingo rw'inyongera runyuramo n'indi ngirabuzima yitwa sedase, naho ubundi poroteyine ihinduka imyanda ikururwa mu maraso, amaherezo igashyirwa mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye n'utugingo tw'ingirabuzimafatizo tw'ubwoko bwa II, ibihaha, uturemangingo tw'igifu, uturemangingo tw'amaraso, uturemangingo tw'amaraso n'utw'imbere mu mubiri, n'uturemangingo tw'uruhu rw'uruhu rw'uruhu mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
ACE2 mRNA kandi iboneka mu gice cy'inyuma cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa striatum, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ubwonko.
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'umuhuza w'imikorere ya ACE.
ACE igabanya imisemburo ya antitansine I mu maraso ikora antitansine II.
ACE2 itandukanya amino acide ya carboxyl-terminal na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayisenya mu gice cy'umuvuduko w'amaraso cyitwa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no kwica izindi peptides zimwe na zimwe zirimo [des-Arg9] - bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 ifasha mu kugabanya umuvuduko w'ibinyamuga bya amino acids SLC6A19 na C bigaragara mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Kubera ko ACE2 ari igipimo cy'indwara, ikora nk'ahantu h'ingenzi ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'indwara zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS) na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhinduranya poroteyine S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 mu byuma bya ACE2 biboneka ku mbuga z'ingirabuzimafatizo, biterwa no gusenya no gusenya aho virusi n'urwungano rwayo biherereye mu byuma by'ingirabuzimafatizo biri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi mikorere yo kwinjiza kandi isaba ko poroteyine S ikenera gufungura TMPRSS2 mu mubiri, ubu bufasha burimo gukorwa ni uburyo bwo kuvura bushobora gukoreshwa.Ibi bikorwa byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, hari inzego zimwe na zimwe n'abahanga mu by'imibereho y'abantu bakomeje gutanga inama yo gukomeza gukoresha ACE inhibitors no kuvurwa na ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buryo bw'isubiramo n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe, bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwerekanye ko gukoresha ACE inhibitors bifitanye isano no kugabanya ibyago 34% byo kurwara ibihaha ugereranyije n'abatarikoresha.
Icyakora, ibyago byo kurwara impyiko byagabanutse ku barwayi bavurwa imiti igabanya imbaraga za ACE, bari basanzwe bafite ibyago byo kurwara impyiko, cyane cyane abafite amarozi, indwara y'imitsi yo mu bwonko n'umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo bifitanye isano no kugabanya igipimo cy'urupfu ruhura n'indwara y'ibihaha, nubwo ingaruka zitari nyinshi cyane kuruta ibyago byo kurwara ibihaha muri rusange.
Ihuriro rya ACE2 (rhACE2) ryifashishwa mu kuvura indwara y'umwijima ikomeye, kandi rituma amaraso atembera neza mu mwijima, ndetse n'umwuka wa ogisijeni ufatanyije na lipopolysaccharide, bigatera ibibazo bikomeye byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Igihe cy'ikirenga cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10, kandi igihe cy'intangiriro y'ibikorwa ni iminota 30 y'inyongera ku gihe cy'iminota 24 cy'igikorwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti mwiza ku bantu batemera uburyo bwo kuvura indwara z'amavunja (RAS) cyangwa mu ndwara z'amavunja aho imikorere y'amavunja abiri yiyongera. RhACE2 yashyizwe mu bikorwa yagenzuwe mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi mu kuvura ibimenyetso bikomeye by'ubuhumekero.
